reviews.reviewText: I purchased this butter dish to replace a broken one. I like this one a lot better. It’s much better made and will fit 2 sticks of butter and it swivels instead of coming apart in 2 pieces. . I also love that it has non-slick grips on the bottom so it doesn’t slide around. An added bonus is the little knife that has a space for its own on top of the dish.
